data.description: Auburn Hills one story home with open floorplan. Generous living area. Island kitchen with tiled backsplash, includes Refrigerator, Stove, Microwave, Dishwasher, and Disposal. Primary bedroom with walk-in closet and full bath. Primary bath with double vanity, separate tub and shower. Privacy fenced backyard with patio slab. Two car attached garage. Community features included swimming Pool, playground park, jogging trails, and sports court. Minutes to Fort Sam Houston and Randolph Air Force Base. Easy access to Loop 1604 and IH-35.
